title: Thomas Barnett from Strike Anywhere
itunes:title: Thomas Barnett from Strike Anywhere
description:
I love Strike Anywhere. You should love Strike Anywhere. I hope after this discussion with the lead vocalist Thomas Barnett, you will. Thomas and I discuss the Richmond, Virginia scene, romantic tour stories and I get to the bottom of why he wears dreadlocks. We also discuss their new EP on Pure Noise Records that smokes. Enjoy!
